{"type":"text","timestamp":1775867231632,"sessionID":"ses_2861243a2ffe2hS31hQs5CzQtz","part":{"id":"prt_d79ef5b97001TPp8af162KKXvz","messageID":"msg_d79ef3b53001tt2FYSymKFmD7c","sessionID":"ses_2861243a2ffe2hS31hQs5CzQtz","type":"text","text":"## AR-021: CLI build 命令 - Archive Summary\n\n### What Was Completed\n\n**1. Core Implementation**\n- ✅ **BuildRuntime** (`agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`) - Full implementation:\n  - `build()` method with local/cloud mode support\n  - `_increment_version()` with semantic versioning (patch & prerelease)\n  - `_validate_build_prerequisites()` (Docker & Dockerfile validation)\n  - `_build_local()` complete implementation\n  - `_update_build_metadata()` with version rollback on failure\n\n- ✅ **DockerService** (`agentcube/services/docker_service.py`) - Full implementation:\n  - `build_image()` with build args and proxy support\n  - `get_image_info()`, `push_image()`, `remove_image()`\n  - Docker registry login and tagging\n\n- ✅ **CLI Integration** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`) - Complete:\n  - `build()` Typer command with all parameters\n  - Error handling with Rich console output\n  - Progress indicators\n\n**2. Test Coverage**\n- ✅ 63 tests (58 passed, 5 skipped)\n- ✅ 99% coverage on `build_runtime.py`\n- ✅ 98% coverage on `docker_service.py`\n- ✅ All unit tests completed\n- ✅ Integration tests defined (skipped by default)\n\n**3. Features Implemented**\n- ✅ Local Docker builds with proxy support\n- ✅ Automatic semantic versioning (patch increment)\n- ✅ Prerelease version handling (alpha.1 → alpha.2)\n- ✅ Build failure version rollback\n- ✅ Metadata validation and updates\n- ✅ Docker availability checks\n- ✅ Build args configuration\n- ✅ Image info retrieval and size formatting\n\n### What Was Deferred\n\n**1. Cloud Build Integration**\n- ⏸️ `_build_cloud()` currently returns stub data only\n- ⏸️ No actual Huawei Cloud SDK integration\n- ⏸️ No multi-cloud provider support (AWS, Aliyun, etc.)\n\n**2. Advanced Features**\n- ⏸️ Multi-architecture builds (AMD64, ARM64)\n- ⏸️ Build cache optimization beyond Docker defaults\n- ⏸️ Build progress notifications (webhooks, email)\n- ⏸️ Custom build timeout configuration\n\n**3. Out of Scope (As Per Original Spec)**\n- Docker daemon installation and configuration\n- Cloud provider SDK implementations\n- Dockerfile generation (handled by `pack` command)\n- Image push functionality (handled by `publish` command)\n\n**Notes**\n- Cloud build infrastructure was marked as \"future enhancement\" in original proposal\n- Integration tests require actual Docker daemon and are marked as optional\n- All core local build functionality is production-ready","time":{"start":1775867231626,"end":1775867231626}}}
